msgid "Choose how preview proxy is mapped: Mode1=Transform, Mode2=Transform+Center offset, Mode3=Bounds remap"
msgstr "选择预览代理的对齐方式：模式1=仅变换，模式2=变换+中心偏移，模式3=包围盒重映射"

